      "id": "ANGULAR_INTERVIEW_QUESTIONS_OUTLINE",
      "title": "Angular Interview Questions Outline",
      "html": "<h1>Complete Angular Interview Questions Coverage</h1>\n<h2>40 Questions Covering the Entire Angular Ecosystem</h2>\n<h3>Part 1: ANGULAR_PRINCIPAL_LEAD_INTERVIEW_QUESTIONS.md (Questions 1-9)</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>✅ Pure Pipes Performance (DETAILED)</li>\n<li>Angular Signals vs RxJS Observables</li>\n<li>RxJS Operators (switchMap, mergeMap, concatMap, exhaustMap)</li>\n<li>Hierarchical Dependency Injection</li>\n<li>Standalone Components Architecture</li>\n<li>Large-Scale Application Architecture</li>\n<li>Error Handling and Logging</li>\n<li>Lazy Loading and Module Federation</li>\n<li>Performance Optimization</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Part 2: ANGULAR_LIFECYCLE_HOOKS_DETAILED.md (Question 10)</h3>\n<ol start=\"10\">\n<li>✅ Lifecycle Hooks Deep Dive (DETAILED)<ul>\n<li>ngOnInit</li>\n<li>ngOnDestroy</li>\n<li>ngOnChanges</li>\n<li>ngAfterViewInit</li>\n<li>ngAfterContentInit</li>\n<li>ngDoCheck</li>\n<li>ngAfterViewChecked/ngAfterContentChecked</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Part 3: ANGULAR_ADVANCED_INTERVIEW_QUESTIONS_PART2.md (Questions 11-30)</h3>\n<ol start=\"11\">\n<li>✅ Server-Side Rendering (SSR) and Hydration (DETAILED)</li>\n<li>✅ HTTP Interceptors and Error Handling (DETAILED)</li>\n<li>Reactive Forms and Validation Patterns</li>\n<li>Angular Security (XSS, CSRF, Sanitization)</li>\n<li>Route Guards and Navigation</li>\n<li>State Management (NgRx, Signals, ComponentStore)</li>\n<li>Testing Strategies (Unit, Integration, E2E)</li>\n<li>Change Detection Strategies (OnPush vs Default)</li>\n<li>Content Projection and ng-content</li>\n<li>Custom Directives and Structural Directives</li>\n<li>Angular Animations</li>\n<li>Dynamic Components and ViewContainerRef</li>\n<li>Angular CDK (Component Dev Kit)</li>\n<li>Internationalization (i18n)</li>\n<li>Progressive Web Apps (PWA) with Angular</li>\n<li>Web Workers and Performance</li>\n<li>Angular Universal and SEO</li>\n<li>RxJS Advanced Patterns</li>\n<li>Memory Leaks and Performance Profiling</li>\n<li>Angular CLI and Build Optimization</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Coverage Areas:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>✅ Core Concepts (Pipes, Lifecycle, Change Detection)</li>\n<li>✅ Performance (SSR, Hydration, Optimization)</li>\n<li>✅ HTTP &amp; Networking (Interceptors, Error Handling)</li>\n<li>🔄 Forms &amp; Validation</li>\n<li>🔄 Security</li>\n<li>🔄 Routing &amp; Navigation</li>\n<li>🔄 State Management</li>\n<li>🔄 Testing</li>\n<li>🔄 Advanced Features (CDK, Animations, PWA)</li>\n<li>🔄 Build &amp; Deployment</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Status:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>✅ Completed: 3 questions with extreme detail</li>\n<li>🔄 In Progress: 27 questions to be added with same level of detail</li>\n<li>Target: All 30 questions with comprehensive, real-world examples</li>\n</ul>\n",
